      "detail": "Accretive/fortifying dynamics mean each generation of training data and model output strengthens the foundation for the next generation. Synthetic data generated by capable models becomes training input for more capable successors in a compounding cycle. The accretive character means early data and capability advantages widen over time through recursive improvement. Data dynamics in AGI development are self-reinforcing in a way that no previous technology investment has exhibited."
    },
