      "detail": "Public/international value capture reflects the principle that AGI benefits should be broadly shared rather than privately concentrated. The magnitude of value created by superhuman general intelligence exceeds any private claim and affects all of humanity. International value sharing mechanisms must be designed before AGI creates irreversible power concentration. Public value capture is the economic expression of the principle that AGI is a common concern of humanity."
